description:
This is a 6 minute workout called '5 Minute Full Body Yoga | QUICK & EASY' from the channel Black Yogi Nico Marie.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Yoga.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Reboot Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Hey, ya'll! Today's video is a 5 MINUTE FULL BODY YOGA practice. This is a short & fairly simple practice that you can do DAILY, whenever you have a few minutes to spare.  Be sure to listen to your body & modify as needed. Come out of any postures that don't feel right & take rests if you need to. Let me know what you think of this video in the comments.  Check out the links below for Black Yogi Nico Marie merch & my DJ channel. Don't forget to LIKE, SHARE, & SUBSCRIBE! Thank you for watching! PEACE & LOVE!
